  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/bbe7a51acc98e22ea53a2de3e6b6a969.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once in a generation, the gods come together to postpone the apocalypse. But this time, the god of communication started a bunch of godly fights and then went awol. With the sky splitting and the gods in disarray, who's gonna join the Bizzyboys to help SAVE DA WORLD FROM A-POCKY-LIPS???</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/4f8c2e64aa06cbe6a7b16cf0bac88b94.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the gods’ mail-carrier, suck up and launch speech bubbles to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/a9af765beeddcf8a8c5382d7e271b092.poster.avif?t=1768595168\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/a9af765beeddcf8a8c5382d7e271b092.webm?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/a9af765beeddcf8a8c5382d7e271b092.mp4?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/60fcee75ae5467692ea280099000d28d.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deliver messages to chat, flirt, or hurt their feelings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/49756842134ebb308c38b3e9956c8504.poster.avif?t=1768595168\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/49756842134ebb308c38b3e9956c8504.webm?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/49756842134ebb308c38b3e9956c8504.mp4?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/165a898f9eb6154459a8c23a6878e721.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The god of TEAMWORK? The god of LOVE SONGS? Drain it, who’s in charge around here…?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/57d04fbfd356c64c6c1d3512a249038d.poster.avif?t=1768595168\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/57d04fbfd356c64c6c1d3512a249038d.webm?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/57d04fbfd356c64c6c1d3512a249038d.mp4?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You may be ready for:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A big colorful world to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Third and first-person gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Weird people. Weirder gods</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >But are you also ready for:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Godly crushes?</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Pumpkin fights??</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Puppets cooking???</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AND YOU’RE NOT READY FOR:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Grovekeeping!</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Godbossing!!</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i><strong>THE END OF THE WORLD AS WE KNOW IT!!!!!</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/9ad49061cc25786a349b18986e2824e8.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/e18e3c6e7a7037853067ecdc0474d9e2.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LimboLane is a creative duo making silly games that squish and bounce, comprised of designer Day Lane and animator Yugo Limbo. They have a love for the kitschy, the surreal, and the utterly bizarre. Their nod-and-shake adventure game <strong>Smile For Me</strong> was self-published on Steam in 2019 and re-released for consoles in 2023.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/bbe7a51acc98e22ea53a2de3e6b6a969.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once in a generation, the gods come together to postpone the apocalypse. But this time, the god of communication started a bunch of godly fights and then went awol. With the sky splitting and the gods in disarray, who's gonna join the Bizzyboys to help SAVE DA WORLD FROM A-POCKY-LIPS???</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/4f8c2e64aa06cbe6a7b16cf0bac88b94.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the gods’ mail-carrier, suck up and launch speech bubbles to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/a9af765beeddcf8a8c5382d7e271b092.poster.avif?t=1768595168\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/a9af765beeddcf8a8c5382d7e271b092.webm?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/a9af765beeddcf8a8c5382d7e271b092.mp4?t=1768595168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840190/extras/60fcee75ae5467692ea280099000d28d.avif?t=1768595168\" width=616 